    "ADInt encompasses 162,212 entities across 113 UMLS semantic types, which after further identification include 25,604 Drugs, 16,474 Diseases, 46,060 Genes and Proteins, 2525 DS, and 128 CIH.",
    "Furthermore, ADInt comprises 1,017,284 triples, capturing 15 distinct relation types.",
    "Detailed statistics can be found in Table 1.",
    "Table 2 presents the performance obtained by various LP methods using the metrics MR, MRR, and Hits@ k 39.",
    "A well-performing model should exhibit a low MR score and high MRR and Hit@k scores."
